1274
00:56:32,972 --> 00:56:36,493
So, like, just looking at advertisements and reading reviews and things, I've kind of pieced

1275
00:56:36,513 --> 00:56:41,254
together my own rollerball game so that I could play it and see what that was like.

1276
00:56:42,174 --> 00:56:45,935
